column3:
Either the patch in this PR or the following should fix the problem (as mentioned in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/20127#issuecomment-706934295):

```diff
diff --git i/contrib/devtools/symbol-check.py w/contrib/devtools/symbol-check.py
index 6949cb7ce..5178ac0d4 100755
--- i/contrib/devtools/symbol-check.py
+++ w/contrib/devtools/symbol-check.py
@@ -45,13 +45,13 @@ MAX_VE
Concept ACK, but I do wonder, why do we run the symbol check on the unit tests?\n\nEdit: oh I guess because they are shipped in the binary release. Never mind.
